8樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾」，不過他在2週前的直播中改口，要大家別當真，笑稱這只是「開玩笑」</strong></span>，要大家輕鬆過日子，強調「我要真幹那事兒，我就不會在鏡頭前說了」、<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「要不6月4號不行，我裸泳得了」</span></strong>。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T18:02:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />估到"},{"pid":"3c3c82467a6695d767668a76792ee8faa9febf5f","tid":2049660,"uid":134012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T18:04:12.000Z","msg":"新中國"},{"pid":"6007054c66064da04fb9dd23624a17bfd5cdf08a","tid":2049660,"uid":286822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T18:05:58.000Z","msg":"宣乜撚<br />\n台灣不嬲都係獨立國家"},{"pid":"6e837270e85601c1aa9dcefff206564447c8382c","tid":2049660,"uid":68837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T18:08:33.000Z","msg":"唉收嗲咪撚燈啦呢件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6f9f37b6afb972db4b4f3bd3634c6fbcf28d556","tid":2049660,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T18:16:28.000Z","msg":"我仲係睇唔到中共點死喎"},{"pid":"b79bfd2c88ffc4f7181cbe180d055cd253725750","tid":2049660,"uid":286309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"700b21a895a41c1c386810a436c5357f1969e3ff","tid":2049660,"uid":130820,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T15:58:21.000Z","msg":"郭文貴當時表示：「2020年是結束共產黨在中國的最後1年，否則文貴就從那18樓跳下去，大家要記住我的承諾。」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T18:17:50.000Z","msg":"18樓跳落17樓"},{"pid":"b129f6bcd396d93f6d361a21e1a32675e808b016","tid":2049660,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T18:20:48.000Z","msg":"美國退出WTO脫離極權國控制既制度<br />\n代表美國即將重建或跳出黎全力打鳩中國<br />\n美國需要盟國支援  <br />\n估計無論有冇國安法  美國今次必要性咁打爆共產黨"},{"pid":"9b116b37821af6fd44d8a478bb36d3f8f0cbdb97","tid":2049660,"uid":89011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime